# Review tooling stays out of the game image: the gallery entry pages are
# served by the tv-gallery sibling image instead (path-routed on the same
# preview host, see scripts/gallery/README.md). Locally the dev server still
# serves them straight from public/. The display test harness itself ships in
# the app bundle regardless (e2e runs against it; inert without URL params).
public/gallery*
